D生活。"},{"pid":"732d91fbdbdd2e135e780fbde6aed3826d77cfc2","tid":1253224,"uid":247175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T23:45:14.000Z","msg":"我都係畢業無工開，轉咗行，但而定重挨緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a5f835ac29dca337a64a2578874bec28f849d8","tid":1253224,"uid":38691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57f6d162d1fb914f3721284637ca13e22677f0bc","tid":1253224,"uid":205734,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f22a132cce5bc9044706eeca0d9c006a12403488","tid":1253224,"uid":194785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:44:41.000Z","msg":"乞食"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"明明入到ha做配藥員有兩皮<br />\n點解乞食呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T23:48:44.000Z","msg":"入到先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e321df737405bbcf269bd531adf3aeba695942f","tid":1253224,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de855fe94e7f42daa1232f247d7f3188ddfbca8d","tid":1253224,"uid":41849,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:15:03.000Z","msg":"點解會有人想做成日輪夜 每日企足八粒鐘 重覆幾個動作成千次既工<br />\n我真係想知 <br />\n以前包有工開有飯食都算啦 而家仲讀果的真係on lun 79"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T00:34:22.000Z","msg":"配藥依類工作遲早畀automation搞撚點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4dfbb1db9a175c8c296342fcee709e819796e9","tid":1253224,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"57f6d162d1fb914f3721284637ca13e22677f0bc","tid":1253224,"uid":205734,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f22a132cce5bc9044706eeca0d9c006a12403488","tid":1253224,"uid":194785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:44:41.000Z","msg":"乞食"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"明明入到ha做配藥員有兩皮<br />\n點解乞食呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T00:39:55.000Z","msg":"晉升階梯極差，藥劑系亦面臨被電腦取代既危機<br />\n<br />\n配藥員未來好快會比科技淘汰架啦，你想入HA不如做護士啦"